{
  "stem": "1929.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'd love to just climb up on those big stacks of timber and I would just sit right on top-- they were high up-- and watch the sky.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I don't remember that much of the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only remember a few streets and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I spent more time-- in, in, in my summer time, my father had a-- had a flour mill and a saw mill I think in partnership with other people, which was like, I don't know, maybe 100 miles away or something like that.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go on a train there and I used to spend my, my summers over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was like I used to go up to the gate and the peasants used to come in with their corn and things to be ground into flour.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I used to take rides on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was-- it wasn't all happy experience, because in the-- in the flour, no, on the timber-- no, not timber.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the saw mill, it was, it was steam driven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day I was there because I was always adventuresome and looking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there and workmen were eating their lunch, sitting down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had these big wheels, like a steering wheel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was playing automobile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I opened up the steam valve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the saw came, came crashing down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got so frightened, you know, that-- You felt lucky you weren't hurt, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't hurt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they-- there were really mean to me, these Polish workers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would-- and also in the flour, because they would throw flour at me, sacks and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
